        </div>


        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="hyakuwariAnswerButton">答え合わせ</button>
        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="hyakuwariResetButton">リセット</button>
        <hr>

        <div id="title">基本計算（ランダム）</div>
        <p>かんたんな計算を練習しよう</p>
        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="setAddButton">たし算をつくる</button>
        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="setSubButton">ひき算をつくる</button>
        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="setMultiButton">かけ算をつくる</button>
        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="setDivideButton">わり算をつくる</button>


        <div class="formula_gyou">
            <div id="formula_container">
                <div id="calc_column0"></div>
                <div class="formula" id="symbol">＋</div>
                <div id="calc_row0"></div>
                <div class="formula">＝</div>
                <input type="tel" class="calc_texts" id="answer" value="" maxlength="3">
            </div>
            <div id="amari_container">
                <div class="formula" id="amari">あまり</div>
                <input type="tel" class="calc_texts" id="left" value="" maxlength="3">
            </div>
        </div>


        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="answerCalcButton">答え合わせ</button>
        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="resetCalcButton">リセット</button>
        <div id="correct_message"></div>

        <h2>筆算メモ</h2>
        <canvas id="canvassample"></canvas>
        <div style="padding:10px">
            <button type="button" class="buttons" id="clearCanvas">リセット</button>
            <button type="button" class="buttons" id="prevCanvas">戻る</button>
            <button type="button" class="buttons" id="nextCanvas">進む</button>
        </div>
        <div style="padding:10px"></div>

        
        <hr>
        <div id="title">表とグラフ</div>
        <p>棒グラフの便利さを実感しよう<br>（テストの点数のグラフ・平均点が出ます）</p>
        <table class="words_table">
            <tr>
                <th class="graph_title">教科</th>
                <th class="label">国語</th>
                <th class="label">算数</th>
                <th class="label">社会</th>
                <th class="label">理科</th>
                <th class="label">英語</th>
            </tr>
            <tr class="words_copy">
                <th class="graph_title">点数</th>
                <td class="score"><input type="tel" class="numbers" value="" maxlength="3" max="100" min="0"></td>
                <td class="score"><input type="tel" class="numbers" value="" maxlength="3" max="100" min="0"></td>
                <td class="score"><input type="tel" class="numbers" value="" maxlength="3" max="100" min="0"></td>
                <td class="score"><input type="tel" class="numbers" value="" maxlength="3" max="100" min="0"></td>
                <td class="score"><input type="tel" class="numbers" value="" maxlength="3" max="100" min="0"></td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="graphButton">グラフ描画</button>
        <div id="stage"></div>


        <hr>
        <div id="title">比例</div>
        <p>□に数字を入力して、比例グラフに親しもう</p>
        <table class="graph">
            <tr>
                <th class="prop_title">x</th>
                <th class="x_points"></th>
                <th class="x_points"></th>
                <th class="x_points"></th>
                <th class="x_points"></th>
                <th class="x_points"></th>
                <th class="x_points"></th>
                <th class="x_points"></th>
                <th class="prop_title">・・・</th>
            </tr>
            <tr class="words_copy">
                <th class="prop_title">y</th>
                <th class="y_points"></th>
                <th class="y_points"></th>
                <th class="y_points"></th>
                <th class="y_points"></th>
                <th class="y_points"></th>
                <th class="y_points"></th>
                <th class="y_points"></th>
                <th class="prop_title">・・・</th>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="prop_container">
            <div class="prop_formula">
                <div class="formula">y</div>
                <div class="formula">＝</div>
                <input type="tel" class="calc_texts" id="prop_num" value="" maxlength="1">
                <div class="formula">x</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="proportionalButton">グラフ描画</button>
        <div class="canvas-container">
            <canvas id="chart1"></canvas>
        </div>


        <hr>
        <div id="title">図形</div>
        <p>長方形（正方形）：たて × よこ ＝ 面積</p>
        <div class="prop_container">
            <div class="prop_formula">
                <input type="tel" class="calc_texts" id="shape_num1" value="" maxlength="2">
                <div class="formula">×</div>
                <input type="tel" class="calc_texts" id="shape_num2" value="" maxlength="2">
                <div class="formula">＝</div>
                <div id="area"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="shapeButton">四角形描画</button>
        <p>これを２つにわったら三角形の面積になる（÷２）</p>
        <div class="prop_container">
            <div class="prop_formula">
                <div id="takasa"></div>
                <div class="formula">×</div>
                <div id="teihen"></div>
                <div class="formula">÷</div>
                <div class="formula">２</div>
                <div class="formula">＝</div>
                <div id="area2"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="triShapeButton">三角形描画</button>
        <div class="canvas-container">
            <canvas id="chart2" width="400" height="400"></canvas>
        </div>


        <hr>
        <div id="title">分数</div>
        <p>□に数字を入力して、分数に親しもう</p>
        <div class="prop_container">
            <div class="prop_formula">
                <input type="tel" class="calc_texts" id="fraction_num" value="" maxlength="2">
                <div class="fraction">分の１</div>
                <div class="formula">＝</div>
                <div id="decimal"></div>
                <div class="formula">＝</div>
                <div id="percent"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button type="button" class="buttons" id="fractionButton">分数描画</button>
        <div id="chart3"></div>
    </div>
</div>
